{"id":440,"title":"看着小清新其实很污的韩国文艺片","image":"http://7xqnv7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/2016-06-14_575feed371a68.jpg","content":"<p><br /></p><p>说到韩国文艺片，大家好像没什么特别的印象。</p><p><br /></p><p>多数韩国文艺片都显得空泛无物，不管是对人性的挖掘还是对心理的表现都略浅。</p><p><br /></p><p>不过，说到<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">特色</strong>的话，就是韩国文艺片总能把<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">污力滔滔</strong>的东西拍得特别<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">小清新</strong>。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xqnv7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/2016-06-14_575fd1ce19843.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 244.399px;\" src=\"http://7xqnv7.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/2016-06-14_575fd1ce19843.jpg\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>特别是在<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">船戏</strong>的剪辑上，显得大胆又含蓄。</p><p><br /></p><p>明明什么都没露，偏偏把人看得面红耳赤。</p><p><br /></p><p>这应该就是船戏的最高境界吧。</p><p><br /></p><p>给大家推荐几部看着小清新其实很污的韩国文艺片。</p><p><br /></p><section style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid transparent; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">1.春夏秋冬又一春</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">봄 여름 가을 겨울 그리고 봄(2003)</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">导演: 金基德</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">主演: 吴永洙 / 金基德 / 金英民</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465897677\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 411.962px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465897677\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>说到韩国文艺片就绕不开<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">金基德</strong>导演。<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>他的镜头有多<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">文艺</strong>，想表达的主题有多<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">深遂</strong>......</p><p><br /></p><p>产生的效果就会有多污。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898073\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 208.727px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898073\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>而且神奇的是大部分镜头你还觉得挺唯美的。</p><p><br /></p><p>这部电影是关于一个和尚的成长故事。<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898110\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 208.727px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898110\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>分成了春夏秋冬四个章节，描绘孩童到老僧的种种<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">七情六欲</strong>。</p><p><br /></p><p>影片用大量<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">山水泼墨画</strong>一般的镜头讲述了一个关于人性的故事。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898224\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 156.893px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898224\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>《芝加哥论坛报》评价本片：<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">“该片是一部像宝石一样的作品。该片丰富地描写了寂静和暴力、圣爱和俗爱、智慧和无差别等主题，几近完美。”</strong><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><section style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid transparent; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; font-size: 20px;\">2.绿洲</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">오아시스(2002)</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">导演: 李沧东</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">主演: 薛景求 / 文素丽 / 安内相</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898737\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 411.962px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898737\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>后来当上韩国文化部长的李沧东导演为观众奉上了一曲<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">凄美之歌</strong>。<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>影片闻不到一点商业气味，但是冲击感却一点也不弱。</p><p><br /></p><p>一个<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">刑满出狱</strong>的边缘人和一个<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">重度脑瘫</strong>患者的爱情故事。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898821\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 154.023px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898821\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>其中有一个情节为最后的悲剧埋下了<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">伏笔</strong>。</p><p><br /></p><p>男主由于一时冲动强暴了女主，但女主却和男主成为了情侣。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898869\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 154.023px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898869\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>而之后，两人再次亲密时却被欺辱女主霸占女主财产的兄嫂看到。</p><p><br /></p><p>男主再此入狱。</p><p><br /></p><p>很难形容这部片子给人什么样的感受，因为导演想表达的东西很丰满也很复杂。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898958\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 160.72px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465898958\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>只是当这部电影最后的时候，已经没人会觉得船戏有什么特别了。</p><p><br /></p><p>反倒是一种<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">沉重的思考</strong>反复萦绕。</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><section style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid transparent; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; font-size: 20px;\">3.密爱</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">밀애(2002)</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">导演: 边永柱</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">主演: 金允珍 / 李宗元 / 河承丽</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br /></strong></p><p><strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465907611\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 343.301px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465907611\" /></strong></p><p><br /></p><p>影片根据小说<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">《在我一生中唯一的特别日子》</strong>改编。<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>讲述了一个<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">背叛</strong>丈夫的妻子，被另一个擅长背叛的男人诱骗的故事。</p><p><br /></p><p>影片在摄影和音乐方面都处理的非常到位。<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465907705\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 154.86px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465907705\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>大胆表现了女性在被<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">压抑</strong>的情形下，如何勇敢的挣脱束缚。</p><p><br /></p><p>这部片子就是非常典型的韩国文艺片，女主极限也只是一个背部全裸而已。</p><p><br /></p><p>但确实挺<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">性感</strong>的（捂脸）。<br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><section style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; border: 1px solid transparent; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);\"><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"word-break: break-all; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; font-size: 20px;\">4.白兰</span></strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.6px;\">파이란(2001)</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">导演: 宋海星</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">主演: 张柏芝 / 崔岷植 / 孔行真</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465904720\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 405.176px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465904720\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>本片是<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">张柏芝</strong>主演的，最后还提名了韩国电影青龙奖<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">最佳女主角</strong>。</p><p><br /></p><p>一个漂泊异乡的中国打工妹，一个浪荡街头的韩国混混。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465904776\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 262.605px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465904776\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>本来是<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">假夫妻</strong>，最后却发生了真感情，重点是两人还都没怎么见过面。</p><p><br /></p><p>影片没有追求表面的花哨，只是讲述平淡而真挚的感情。</p><p><br /></p><p><img data-ke-src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465904834\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 191.333px;\" src=\"http://7xrap3.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/1465904834\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>近乎陌生的两人却通过合理的安排将感情联系了起来。</p><p><br /></p><p>这部片子里有最美好的张柏芝和<strong style=\"line-height: 25.6px; color: rgb(171, 25, 66); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\">离奇又合理</strong>的爱。<br /></p>"}